headline: Firing on All Cylinders: Shopify (NYSE:SHOP) Q4 Earnings Lead the Way
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Shopify (NYSE:SHOP) and the best and worst performers in the e-commerce software industry.
